      <title>台湾总统卫队开枪自杀；新的咨询承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/taiwan-presidential-guard-shoots-himself-new-counseling-pledged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五晚上，台湾总统府一名武装警卫在执勤期间自杀，此后总统府承诺加强咨询服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/taiwan-presidential-guard-shoots-himself-new-counseling-pledged</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:33:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称美国将在人道主义危机中空投加沙援助物资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/biden-says-us-to-airdrop-gaza-aid-as-humanitarian-crisis-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统宣布，美国将开始向加沙空投人道主义援助，与其他国家一道，以缓解以色列与哈马斯战争造成的日益严峻的局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/biden-says-us-to-airdrop-gaza-aid-as-humanitarian-crisis-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁弗林表示，他在游说反对工资法案的过程中会见了纽瑟姆的工作人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/flynn-says-he-met-with-newsom-staff-in-group-lobbying-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁格雷格·弗林(Greg Flynn)在加州拥有两打帕内拉面包(Panera Bread)特许经营店，他表示，他建议将快餐休闲餐厅排除在提高该州快餐工人最低工资的法案之外，但当生产和销售面包的连锁店被特别豁免时，他感到惊讶从最终的立法来看。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/flynn-says-he-met-with-newsom-staff-in-group-lobbying-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克誓言英国在加洛韦获胜后镇压加沙抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/sunak-vows-uk-crackdown-on-protests-over-gaza-after-galloway-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克警告说，伊斯兰主义者和极右极端分子正在破坏英国民主，他敦促警方对以色列-哈马斯战争以来的抗议游行采取更强硬的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/sunak-vows-uk-crackdown-on-protests-over-gaza-after-galloway-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:06:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织将延长电子商务关税暂停两年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/wto-set-to-extend-moratorium-on-e-commerce-tariffs-for-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在阿布扎比进行马拉松式谈判后，世界贸易组织暂时同意延长暂停征收电子商务关税，但农业和渔业补贴等其他关键贸易问题仍未解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/wto-set-to-extend-moratorium-on-e-commerce-tariffs-for-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 18:25:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在佛罗里达州的秘密记录审判可能会被推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/trump-s-florida-trial-on-secret-records-will-likely-be-postponed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州的一名联邦法官表示，唐纳德·特朗普因机密文件处理不当而受到的审判可能会从目前的 5 月 20 日开始推迟，这使得他在再次竞选白宫之际的法律时间表陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/trump-s-florida-trial-on-secret-records-will-likely-be-postponed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 18:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>商人告诉法官他用梅赛德斯贿赂了梅南德斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/businessman-tells-judge-he-bribed-senator-menendez-for-favors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名商人承认密谋用一辆奔驰贿赂美国参议员鲍勃·梅南德斯以换取好处，并暗示他将在针对新泽西州民主党人的庞大腐败案件中与检察官合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/businessman-tells-judge-he-bribed-senator-menendez-for-favors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 18:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰将获得捷克主导的155毫米炮弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/ukraine-to-get-155mm-artillery-shells-found-in-czech-led-scouring-of-stockpiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军方将接收第一批可能有数十万枚 155 毫米炮弹，作为国际社会寻找外国储备的努力的一部分，而美国提供更多援助的努力仍悬而未决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/ukraine-to-get-155mm-artillery-shells-found-in-czech-led-scouring-of-stockpiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 17:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普接近提名，黑利批评共和党的优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/haley-criticizes-gop-priorities-as-trump-closes-in-on-nomination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 感叹共和党的方向——声称它已经放弃了小政府和自由市场的核心原则——竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普即将获得提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/haley-criticizes-gop-priorities-as-trump-closes-in-on-nomination</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 15:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔治·加洛韦的复出考验英国因加沙战争而陷入的激烈政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/george-galloway-s-comeback-tests-uk-s-febrile-politics-over-israel-hamas-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[左翼连续破坏者乔治·加洛韦重返议会，给本已激烈的英国政坛带来了更多波动，因为以色列与哈马斯的战争颠覆了社区凝聚力，各党派在冲突问题上努力寻求一个不疏远支持者的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/george-galloway-s-comeback-tests-uk-s-febrile-politics-over-israel-hamas-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 14:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
